The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Will use Souravs experience
                                                     Will use Souravs experience
            LOKENDRA PRATAP SAHI            McCullum                           
	Cape Town: Brendon McCullum, the Kolkata Knight Riders new captain, briefly spoke to The Telegraph on Friday evening.               
	The following are excerpts         
	Im happy with my promotion... Yeah, I was hoping Id get the captaincy and I got the news yesterday (Thursday)... Ive spoken to Sourav Ganguly and Ill be using his experience as much as I can... Hes fine... Hes taken it well... Weve got a challenge ahead of us and, now, its a question of the team delivering...         
	McCullum is the New Zealand vice-captain.                                                                                                                       
